column5: From Blizzard  Did it start to freeze as you were pulling it out John?
Still makes me drool, even when they're frozen solid
Still makes me drool, even when they're frozen solid  And over a 1000 km away. LOL

It sure is nice to read about some fish being caught. Wormdunker and I were thinking about hitting Quinte. That is until I found out he runs and guns drilling holes and doesn't have a 2 man Clam. No way no how I am roughing it like we did 40 years ago. I want 5 star accommodations out there at my age. I'm impressed with both his fitness and passion, something I lost a few surgeries ago.
Can we get a thread going to teach John how to use photobucket?????  Nice fish bud!!!
Your sushi is ready. Nice fish
Is that still intact and frozen John? Can I borrow it? I have a couple laker ice derbies coming up.
Can we get a thread going to teach John how to use photobucket?  Nice fish bud!!!   Not that we dont mind helpping a northern brother.
